---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="页面不存在 | River Notes" description="你访问的页面不存在。">
  <section class="shell listing-hero fade-up">
    <p class="eyebrow">404</p>
    <h1>这页还没被整理出来。</h1>
    <p>可以先回到首页，或者去题解归档继续逛逛。</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="button button-primary" href="/">返回首页</a>
      <a class="button button-secondary" href="/blog">前往归档</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
